{"tid":1493544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[推Post啦屌你]824!觀塘要人 824!觀塘要人 824!觀塘要人","createTime":"2019-08-21T09:32:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T04:23:17.000Z","uid":40697,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"046d82c3397b85c6903dcab5a078258a96e5c7f9","tid":1493544,"uid":40697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sYNQeMK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsYNQeMK.png&h=3cb48414&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LpXTWZ5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLpXTWZ5.png&h=7a122f0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r2kuvj6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr2kuvj6.png&h=e30a01e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AbE3zMM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAbE3zMM.png&h=ff5c0e94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nForward:<br />\n真係要分享:<br />\n我咪話我個同事個妹番大陸比人捉左, 事隔2日終於番到香港, 聽番成件事先知有幾恐怖.<br />\n1. 原來佢當日已經無帶自己電話, 係帶左公司電話 (相信係無示威資料), 佢當日過關係大陸職員一scan 張回鄉證, 就出左alert 要帶去第2間房。<br />\n2. 事後知道alert既原因係因為佢去左示威( Not 前線), 佢一直極力否認佢有參與示威, 直到公安拎左一張佢參與示威 (應該係搞中聯辦果日)既高清大頭相, 問呢個係咪你嚟, 果刻佢已經無得否認。<br />\n3. 最恐怖既地方, 公安問佢有無Telegram, 佢再一次極力否認, 然後公安問佢, 你tg 既ac 係咪叫xxxxx (佢tg 個名)<br />\n4. 到最後佢可以番香港, 但係要交哂fb tg ig 既ac &amp; PW<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n總結: <br />\n1. 就算唔係前線, 出得去一定要遮樣 (口罩, 頭套, 臉罩), 因為香港已經無私隱可言<br />\n2. 呢1年無咩事都唔好番大陸, 因為已經唔係電話有咩資料事, 而係你唔知自己有無比人影到大頭相.<br />\n3. 已經可以肯定tg有大陸係到滲透緊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>反監控呀屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"6f0bdc48a6223c244486da9b1d86c0d2d3b9afed","tid":1493544,"uid":40697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-21T09:33:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d353d6c40